data.description: NO HOA! Discover Merritt Island charm at 1500 Dorsal Street, a meticulously renovated gem in a tranquil neighborhood. This mid-century modern home features two luxurious master suites, an open floor plan, and top-tier bathrooms, combining elegance with comfort. The heart of the home is a stunning kitchen, ideal for culinary adventures. Outdoors, the private saltwater pool, fenced for privacy, offers a perfect retreat for relaxation and entertainment. Strategically located close to Boat Ramps, beautiful beaches, and space industry giants, it's a convenient paradise. Just minutes from Cocoa Beach and Port Canaveral, this home is perfect as a family residence or an investment opportunity. Enjoy a Florida lifestyle with indoor laundry, an oversized shed, new gutters, and ample carport space. Experience Merritt Island's best at your doorstep, with a short drive to Orlando. Schedule your private showing today for this turnkey Merritt Island beauty.Step out side an watch the rockets launch
